import React from "react";
import { TextField, Button } from "@material-ui/core";

function DadosEntrega(){
    return(
        <form>
            <TextField
                id="cep"
                label="CEP"
                type="text"
                variant="outlined"
                fullWidth
                margin="normal"
            />
            <TextField
                id="address"
                label="EndereÃ§o"
                type="text"
                variant="outlined"
                fullWidth
                margin="normal"
            />
            
             <Button
                variant="contained"
                color="primary"
                type="submit"
                fullWidth
            >
                Cadastrar
            </Button>
        </form>
    )    
}

export default DadosEntrega;
